                        necessary. Please review our Refund Policy carefully.</p>

                    <h2>1. Eligibility for Refunds</h2>
                    <p>Refunds may be granted under the following conditions:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>No Work Initiated:</strong> If you request a refund before any design work has
                            started, a full refund will be issued.</li>
                        <li><strong>Non-Delivery of Service:</strong> If Monkeysingh.com fails to deliver the service
                            due to unforeseen circumstances (e.g., technical issues, unavailability of resources), you
                            are entitled to a full refund.</li>
                        <li><strong>Incomplete Projects:</strong> If the project is cancelled after work has commenced
                            but before completion, Monkeysingh.com may offer a partial refund, depending on the amount
                            of work completed.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>2. Non-Refundable Conditions</h2>
                    <p>Refunds will not be provided under the following circumstances:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Change of Mind:</strong> If the design work has already commenced and you change
                            your mind about the project, no refund will be provided.</li>
                        <li><strong>Completed Projects:</strong> Once the project has been delivered and approved by
                            you, no refunds will be issued.</li>
                        <li><strong>Dissatisfaction After Revisions:</strong> If you are unhappy with the design after
                            revisions are made within the scope agreed upon in the project, no refund will be granted.
                            We encourage open communication during the revision process to ensure your satisfaction.
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>3. Revision and Correction Process</h2>
                    <p>Monkeysingh.com provides clients with a set number of revisions as part of the design process. If
                        you request additional revisions beyond the agreed scope, additional fees may apply, and these
                        are non-refundable.</p>

                    <h2>4. Refund Process</h2>
                    <p>To request a refund, please follow these steps:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@monkeysingh.com">support@monkeysingh.com</a> with your
                            request, including your project details and reason for the refund.</li>
                        <li>Refund requests must be made within 7 days of the initial project payment.</li>
                        <li>If eligible, refunds will be processed within 10 business days via the original payment
                            method used.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>5. Disputes</h2>
